  "title": "AI Usage Log Table Indexes",
  "content": {
    "type": "factual",
    "format": "markdown",
    "body": "Three indexes are created on the `ai_usage_log` table: `idx_ai_usage_user` (on `user_id`, `called_at` DESC), `idx_ai_usage_feature` (on `feature`, `called_at` DESC), and `idx_ai_usage_provider` (on `provider`, `called_at` DESC)."
